    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You've been trained in the ancestral weapons of Othard and Hingashi. You gain access to all uncommon weapons from Hingashi (the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Y1dkRsRd1Z7Jf2y6]{Katana}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.YOpopjoWgU7bkmwh]{Wakizashi}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.NufKswitJjxDCX8f]{Naginata} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.KtarUneAx0hibGtW]{Nodachi}). You have familiarity with weapons from Hingashi - for the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.</p><p>At 5th level, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.</p>",
